    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="My-New-Post"><a href="#My-New-Post" class="headerlink" title="My New Post"></a>My New Post</h1><p>[toc]</p><h3 id="一、官网安装稳定版本node"><a href="#一、官网安装稳定版本node" class="headerlink" title="一、官网安装稳定版本node"></a>一、官网安装稳定版本node</h3><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/</a></p><p>检查是否安装好</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="二、注册github"><a href="#二、注册github" class="headerlink" title="二、注册github"></a>二、注册github</h3><p>选择<code>create a project</code></p><p><img src="./src/git1.png" alt=""></p><p>建好以后做一个测试，点击<code>create a new file</code></p><p>新建一个<code>index.html</code>文件</p><p><img src="./src/git2.png" alt=""></p><p>保存提交，点击<code>commit new file</code></p><p>浏览器中打开<code>lxrlxrlxr2.github.io</code></p><h3 id="三、官网下载git"><a href="#三、官网下载git" class="headerlink" title="三、官网下载git"></a>三、官网下载git</h3><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://git-scm.com/downloads</a></p><p>检查是否安装好</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="四、githubSSH配置"><a href="#四、githubSSH配置" class="headerlink" title="四、githubSSH配置"></a>四、githubSSH配置</h3><ul><li><p>安装路径下打开git</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"140*****62@qq.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以直接一直回车</p></li><li><p>打开github / settings / SSH and GPG keys</p><p>点击<code>New SSH key</code></p><p>title : 随便写</p><p>key : <code>C:\Users\Alice\.ssh\id_rsa.pub</code></p><p>点击<code>Add</code>，即完成</p></li></ul><h3 id="五、本地hexo"><a href="#五、本地hexo" class="headerlink" title="五、本地hexo"></a>五、本地hexo</h3><p>官方文档 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></p><p>新建文件夹，cmd到文件夹内</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="六、hexo发布到github上"><a href="#六、hexo发布到github上" class="headerlink" title="六、hexo发布到github上"></a>六、hexo发布到github上</h3><ul><li><p>将文件夹在编辑器中打开</p></li><li><p>打开_config.yml文件</p><ul><li><p>修改<code># Deployment</code></p><p><code>repo</code>在仓库中复制链接🔗</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;lxrlxrlxr&#x2F;lxrlxrlxr2.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改<code># URL</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url: https://lxrlxrlxr2.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改<code># Site</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: lxr_blog</span><br><span class="line">author: 大瑞</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>本地执行</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s -p</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装插件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>配置github信息</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">"140*****62@qq.com"</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">"lxr"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>生成提交命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="./src/git4.png" style="zoom: 67%;" /></li><li><p>打开网址即可</p></li></ul><h3 id="七、换主题"><a href="#七、换主题" class="headerlink" title="七、换主题"></a>七、换主题</h3><p><a href="https://hexo.bootcss.com/themes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.bootcss.com/themes/</a></p>]]></content>
    
